Nanjo: To think you were a{nl}
gambler. You really can't{nl}
judge a person by looks.{waitkey}{ret}

Nanjo: What a happy-go-lucky{nl}
fool. To be so at ease at a{nl}
time like this — almost{nl}
enviable.{waitkey}{ret}

Mark: Elly's quite the{nl}
celebrity, huh!{waitkey}{clearbox}Guess it's only natural,{nl}
looking as good as she does.{waitkey}{ret}

Mark: I don't mind a casino{nl}
myself, but right now I wanna{nl}
hit the shrine first.{waitkey}{ret}

Yukino: I don't care what you{nl}
do, but could you do it after{nl}
we go to the hospital?{waitkey}{ret}

Yukino: Eriko's fearlessness{nl}
leaves me speechless. But{nl}
then, she does look the part.{waitkey}{ret}

Clerk: Welcome~ Here we{nl}
exchange money for coins~♥{waitkey}{clearbox}Shall we change your money{nl}
into coins?{nl}
