Customer: Oh, you guys St.{nl}
Hermelin students? Then you{nl}
must know that girl{waitkey}{clearbox}Long hair, great figure,{nl}
goes by Sally or Mary or{nl}
something...{waitkey}{clearbox}She's a real beauty, huh.{nl}
Hey, introduce me sometime!{waitkey}{ret}

Customer: Ah, I was looking{nl}
for you. You shouldn't be{nl}
wandering around!{waitkey}{clearbox}With demons out and all, it's{nl}
scary, right? I was thinking{nl}
I'd protect you!{waitkey}{ret}

Elly: Why, thank you...{waitkey}{clearbox}But when it comes to Demons,{nl}
I have more knowledge than{nl}
you do,{waitkey}{clearbox}and I can look after myself,{waitkey}so no{wait_fr:21} thank{wait_fr:21} you!{waitkey}{ret}

Customer: Isn't there a girl{nl}
called Elly? And here I was{nl}
gonna show off how manly{nl}
I am...{waitkey}{ret}

Customer: Tch, that didn't{nl}
pan out.{waitkey}But she'll start whining{nl}
about being scared of demons{nl}
soon enough! Till then, I{nl}
keep at it!{waitkey}{ret}

Customer: Aw man, I blew it{nl}
all again!{waitkey}{clearbox}I sank a lot in, so if the{nl}
next guy to play hits a win,{nl}
he gets the bargain, huh.{waitkey}{clearbox}Ah! Don't tell me you're{nl}
gonna play next?! Argh, no{nl}
fair!{waitkey}{ret}

A poker game where you can{nl}
swap cards just once.{waitkey}{clearbox}First, you are dealt{nl}
five cards.{waitkey}{clearbox}Use the D-Pad to pick the{nl}
cards you want to keep,{waitkey}then press ○, ×, △ or □{nl}
to HELD (lock) them.{waitkey}{clearbox}Once your HELD cards are set,{nl}
press R1 or R2 to{nl}
re-DRAW,{waitkey}and the rest are swapped out.{waitkey}{clearbox}After the re-DRAW, if you've{nl}
formed a hand, you win.{waitkey}{clearbox}The more you bet, the bigger{nl}
the payout (ODDS) when{nl}
you complete a hand.{waitkey}{clearbox}Also, when you form a hand,{nl}
you can wager that payout{nl}
in an Extra Game.{waitkey}{clearbox}If you'd rather skip the{nl}
Extra Game, choose TAKE SCORE.{waitkey}{clearbox}There are 3 Extra Games, and{nl}
in each, every win doubles{nl}
your payout.{waitkey}{clearbox}By winning on and on, the{nl}
Extra Game payout can climb{nl}
as high as 1,000,000.{waitkey}{clearbox}But beware: one single loss{nl}
forfeits the entire payout{nl}
you had built up.{waitkey}{clearbox}<Extra Game 1>{nl}
- HI&LOW{waitkey}{clearbox}One card is shown face up,{nl}
and four face down{nl}
on the screen.{waitkey}{clearbox}From the four face-down{nl}
cards, pick one higher than{nl}
the face-up card.{waitkey}{clearbox}If your card ties the face-up{nl}
card, it's a draw and you{nl}
try again.{waitkey}{clearbox}<Extra Game 2>{nl}
- BIG&SMALL{waitkey}{clearbox}One card is shown face up{nl}
and one face down{nl}
on the screen.{waitkey}{clearbox}Guess whether the face-down{nl}
card is bigger or smaller{nl}
than the face-up one.{waitkey}{clearbox}Beware: if your card ties the{nl}
face-up card, you lose.{waitkey}{clearbox}<Extra Game 3>{nl}
- RED&BLACK{waitkey}{clearbox}One card is shown face down{nl}
on the screen.{waitkey}{clearbox}If you think the face-down{nl}
card is a Heart or Diamond,{nl}
choose "RED".{waitkey}{clearbox}If it's a Spade or Club,{nl}
choose "BLACK".{waitkey}{clearbox}If your color matches the{nl}
card's color, you win.{waitkey}{ret}

