WIN:{nl}
When your total stays{nl}
under 21{waitkey}and beats the dealer's total,{nl}
or the dealer busts.{waitkey}{clearbox}B.JACK:{nl}
(Blackjack){nl}
An Ace plus any 10-K,{waitkey}a two-card combo{nl}
(you STAND automatically).{waitkey}After a SPLIT it's not a{nl}
Blackjack and counts as 21.{waitkey}{clearbox}6CARDS:{nl}
When you STAND with six{nl}
cards{waitkey}without going over 21.{waitkey}{clearbox}7CARDS:{nl}
When seven cards drawn{nl}
stay under 21{waitkey}(you STAND automatically).{waitkey}{clearbox}Hrt/Clb/Dia A&J:{nl}
An A-and-J Blackjack where{nl}
both cards' suits{waitkey}are Heart, Club or Diamond.{waitkey}{clearbox}Spd A&J:{nl}
An A-and-J Blackjack where{nl}
both cards' suits{waitkey}are Spades.{waitkey}{clearbox}777:{nl}
When both dealt cards are 7,{nl}
you HIT a third{waitkey}and draw another 7.{waitkey}{ret}

A slot machine made of five{nl}
big drums and 16{nl}
small drums.{waitkey}{clearbox}The more coins you bet, the{nl}
more lines you play{nl}
for a win.{waitkey}{clearbox}You can bet up to{nl}
eight coins.{waitkey}{clearbox}Bets 1/2/5/6 use horizontal{nl}
lines, bets 3/4/7/8 use{nl}
vertical lines to judge.{waitkey}{clearbox}Note: bets 5-8 give two{nl}
judging lines{nl}
per bet.{waitkey}{clearbox}When the game starts, all{nl}
the big and small drums{nl}
begin to spin.{waitkey}{clearbox}After they spin a while,{nl}
the small drums stop first{nl}
(the big drums keep spinning).{waitkey}{clearbox}Pressing ○, ×, △ or □{nl}
shifts the small drums{nl}
clockwise.{waitkey}{clearbox}Shift the small drums well{nl}
to line the symbols up{nl}
more easily.{waitkey}{clearbox}Once you've set the small{nl}
drums, press R1 or R2 and{nl}
the big drums stop.{waitkey}{clearbox}If three or more symbols{nl}
line up on a bet line,{nl}
you win.{waitkey}{clearbox}Bets 1-4 line up to five,{nl}
bets 5-8 line up to four{nl}
symbols each.{waitkey}{clearbox}Also, if the big drums'{nl}
symbols line up diagonally,{nl}
at the 4 corners, or all over,{waitkey}you win regardless of the{nl}
line you bet.{waitkey}{clearbox}A win on the big drums{nl}
multiplies the payout by{nl}
your bet amount.{waitkey}{ret}

