The key to this game is{nl}
spotting where both the row{nl}
and column score a HIT (H).{waitkey}{clearbox}When you find a spot that{nl}
hits on both, mark it{nl}
for now.{waitkey}{clearbox}Also, the RESULT showing your{nl}
past entries is a big hint,{nl}
so use it for reference.{waitkey}{ret}
